{"article_id":"sxoFKvuJM7OmflAz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Tsarnaev has said","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"his brother drove the attack","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"and they had no international ties","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Federal investigators return Boylston Street to city of Boston","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"but it remains closed","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"His brother was killed during a police chase early Friday","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Boston Marathon bombing suspect Dzhokhar Tsarnaev has told investigators","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"his older brother Tamerlan was the driving force behind last week 's attack","depth":13},{"id":9,"text":"and that no international terrorist groups were behind them ,","depth":13},{"id":10,"text":"a U.S. government source said Monday .","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"Preliminary interviews with Tsarnaev indicate","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"the two brothers fit the classification of self-radicalized jihadists ,","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"the source said .","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"Dzhokhar Tsarnaev ,","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"wounded","depth":14},{"id":16,"text":"and held in a Boston hospital ,","depth":14},{"id":17,"text":"has said","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"his brother","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"-- who was killed early Friday --","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"wanted to defend Islam from attack ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"according to the source .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"The government source cautioned","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that the interviews were preliminary ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"and that Tsarnaev 's account needs to be checked out","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"and followed up on by investigators .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"And a federal law enforcement official told CNN","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"while investigators have seen nothing yet","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"to indicate","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"the suspects were working with anyone else ,","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"a lot of work remains","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"before they can say confidently","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"that no others were involved .","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"That official would not comment on any motive or specifics on what Dzhokhar Tsarnaev has communicated to officials .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"The 19-year-old has been charged with using and conspiring to use a weapon of mass destruction","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"resulting in death ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"and one count of malicious destruction of property by means of an explosive device","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"resulting in death .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"He was heavily sedated and on a ventilator at Beth Israel Deaconess Hospital ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"but was `` alert , mentally competent and lucid '' during the brief initial court appearance at his bedside on Monday ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"U.S. Magistrate Judge Marianne Bowler found .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"During the hearing , Tsarnaev communicated mostly by nodding his head ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"though he once answered `` No ''","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"when Bowler asked him","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"if he could afford a lawyer ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"according to a transcript of the proceeding .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"A public defender was appointed","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"to represent him .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Investigators have been asking Tsarnaev","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"whether there are more bombs , explosives caches or weapons beyond those","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"already found by police , and if anyone else was involved in the attacks ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"a source with first-hand knowledge of the investigation told CNN .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Investigators are going into Tsarnaev 's room every few hours","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"to ask questions in the presence of doctors ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"the source said .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Federal agents at first questioned Tsarnaev","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"without reading him his Miranda rights , under an exception to the rule","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"invoked","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"when authorities believe","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"there is an imminent public safety threat ,","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"a Justice Department official said over the weekend .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"But by the time of the hospital room proceeding ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"government sources said","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"he had been read his rights ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"and Bowler reviewed those with him again Monday .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Tsarnaev had been shot in the head , neck , legs and one hand ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"according to an FBI affidavit","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"supporting the charges .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"He had lost a lot of blood","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"and may have hearing loss from two flash-bang devices","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"used to draw him out of the boat ,","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"the source said .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"-- armed with handguns and explosives --","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"apparently were planning another attack","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"before the shootout disrupted their efforts .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"It was n't clear whether Tsarnaev was wounded during his capture Friday night or in an earlier shootout with police","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"that left his 26-year-old brother dead .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Boston Police Commissioner Ed Davis said","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"the brothers","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"-- armed with handguns and explosives --","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"apparently were planning another attack","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"before the shootout disrupted their efforts .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"`` I believe","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"that the only reason","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that someone would have those in their possession","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"was to further attack people","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"and cause more death and destruction , ''","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Davis said on CNN 's `` Starting Point '' Monday .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"Investigators are also trying to determine","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"whether anyone else was involved in the bombings .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"But Davis ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"speaking Sunday to CNN 's Don Lemon ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"that he was confident","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"that the brothers were `` the two major actors in the violence","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"that occurred . '' `` I told the people of Boston","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"that they can rest easily ,","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"that the two people","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"who were committing these vicious attacks","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"are either dead or arrested ,","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"and I still believe that , ''","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"Meanwhile , after a week of combing the downtown thoroughfare","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"where the bombs went off for evidence ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"federal authorities handed control of Boylston Street back to the city .","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"But the blocks around the bomb sites remain closed to the public","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"while Boston officials clean up the area","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"and make sure","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"the buildings are safe","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"to occupy .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"`` This area will be opened up to businesses over the next few hours ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"and then the people will be back here in a day or so , ''","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"Davis said .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"`` And they will be walking up and down this street ,","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"and the terrorists will understand","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"that they can not keep us down . ''","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"A police honor guard ,","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"accompanied by a bagpiper ,","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"lowered the flag","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"that had flown at the finish line of last week 's marathon","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"and presented it to Mayor Thomas Menino","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"to mark the occasion .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"Shortly afterward , workers in bright yellow suits began hosing down","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"and scrubbing the sidewalks around the second bomb site .","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"Among the pieces of evidence","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"collected from Boylston Street during the past week","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"was a tree","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"that Dzhokhar Tsarnaev may have leaned against before the bombing ,","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"according to a source","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"who receives regular intelligence briefings on the Boston bombings .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"The source said","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"the tree","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"-- located at the site of the second blast --","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"was removed along with the surrounding grate ,","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"where the explosive device 's circuit board was found .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"The decision","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"to charge Tsarnaev in civilian court","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"put an end to speculation","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"that he would be charged as an enemy combatant , a designation","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"sometimes used against terrorists .","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"White House spokesman Jay Carney said","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"that Tsarnaev is a naturalized U.S. citizen","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"and can not be tried by a military commission .","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"Trying Tsarnaev in civilian courts","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"-- like `` hundreds of terrorists '' to date --","depth":15},{"id":146,"text":"is `` absolutely the right way","depth":16},{"id":147,"text":"to go","depth":16},{"id":148,"text":"and the appropriate way","depth":16},{"id":149,"text":"to go , ''","depth":16},{"id":150,"text":"Carney said .","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"`` We have a long history","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"of successfully prosecuting terrorists","depth":15},{"id":153,"text":"and bringing them to justice ,","depth":15},{"id":154,"text":"and the president fully believes","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"that that process will work in this case . ''","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"That disappointed Sen. Lindsey Graham , R-South Carolina ,","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"who has been calling for Tsarnaev to be handed over to U.S. intelligence as an `` enemy combatant . ''","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"`` There is ample evidence here on the criminal side , ''","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"Graham said .","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"`` A first-year law student could prosecute this case .","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"What I am worried about is , what does this individual know about future attacks or terrorist organizations","depth":15},{"id":162,"text":"that may be in our midst ?","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"We have the right","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"to gather intelligence . ''","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"Graham also said","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"there was also `` ample evidence ''","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"that the bombings were `` inspired by radical ideology . ''","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"But","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"while Tamerlan Tsarnaev apparently became increasingly radical in the past three or four years ,","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"according to an analysis of his social media accounts and the recollections of family members ,","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"there was no evidence Monday","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"that he had any active association with international jihadist groups .","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"Tamerlan Tsarnaev , 26 , died after a shootout with police early Friday .","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"Dzhokhar Tsarnaev was captured that night ,","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"after police found him hiding in a boat in the back yard of a house in the Boston suburb of Watertown , Massachusetts .","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"With one suspect dead","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"and the other hindered in his ability","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"to communicate ,","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"investigators are eager to speak to Tamerlan Tsarnaev 's wife , Katherine Russell ,","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"to see","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"what she might know about incidents","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"leading up to the bombings .","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"On Monday , her attorney said","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"she learned of her husband 's alleged involvement through news accounts .","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"`` She knew nothing about it at any time , ''","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"Amato DeLuca said in response to questions","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"about whether Russell knew of plans","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"to attack the marathon .","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"Tsarnaev stayed home","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"and cared for the couple 's 2-year-old daughter","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"while his wife worked long hours as a home-care aide ,","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"according to DeLuca .","depth":9},{"id":193,"text":"`` They 're very distraught .","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"They 're upset .","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"Their lives have been unalterably changed .","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"They 're upset","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"because of what happened ,","depth":14},{"id":198,"text":"the people","depth":15},{"id":199,"text":"that were injured ,","depth":16},{"id":200,"text":"that were killed .","depth":16},{"id":201,"text":"It 's an awful , terrible thing , ''","depth":10},{"id":202,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"`` And of course","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"( for ) Katy , it 's even worse","depth":10},{"id":205,"text":"because what she lost","depth":10},{"id":206,"text":"-- her husband and the father of her daughter . ''","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"The Tsarnaev family hails from the Russian republic of Chechnya","depth":8},{"id":208,"text":"and fled the brutal wars there in the 1990s .","depth":8},{"id":209,"text":"The two brothers were born in Kyrgyzstan ;","depth":8},{"id":210,"text":"Dzhokhar became a U.S. citizen in 2012 ,","depth":9},{"id":211,"text":"while Tamerlan was a legal U.S. resident .","depth":9},{"id":212,"text":"An FBI official said","depth":8},{"id":213,"text":"agents interviewed Tamerlan Tsarnaev in 2011 at the request of the Russian government .","depth":8},{"id":214,"text":"The FBI said","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"Russia claimed","depth":11},{"id":216,"text":"that he was a follower of radical Islam","depth":12},{"id":217,"text":"and that he had changed drastically since 2010 .","depth":12},{"id":218,"text":"But the Russian government 's request was vague ,","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"a U.S. official and a law enforcement source said Sunday .","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"The lack of specifics limited how much the FBI was able to investigate Tamerlan ,","depth":9},{"id":221,"text":"the law enforcement official said .","depth":9},{"id":222,"text":"In August 2012 ,","depth":7},{"id":223,"text":"soon after returning from a visit to Russia ,","depth":8},{"id":224,"text":"the elder Tsarnaev brother created a YouTube channel with links to a number of videos .","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"Two videos under a category","depth":9},{"id":226,"text":"labeled `` Terrorists ''","depth":9},{"id":227,"text":"were deleted .","depth":8},{"id":228,"text":"It 's not clear when or by whom .","depth":7},{"id":229,"text":"Tamerlan Tsarnaev attended prayers periodically at the Islamic Society of Boston 's mosque in Cambridge ,","depth":7},{"id":230,"text":"a board member told CNN 's Brian Todd .","depth":7},{"id":231,"text":"In a statement","depth":11},{"id":232,"text":"issued Monday , the society said","depth":11},{"id":233,"text":"he twice interrupted sermons","depth":13},{"id":234,"text":"-- once in November","depth":14},{"id":235,"text":"to express his opposition to celebrating any holiday as un-Islamic ,","depth":14},{"id":236,"text":"and once in January","depth":13},{"id":237,"text":"when he tore into the preacher","depth":14},{"id":238,"text":"for citing civil rights leader Martin Luther King .","depth":14},{"id":239,"text":"The second time , the congregation shouted back ,","depth":13},{"id":240,"text":"`` Leave now , ''","depth":13},{"id":241,"text":"the statement said .","depth":12},{"id":242,"text":"`` After the sermon and the congregational prayer ended ,","depth":11},{"id":243,"text":"a few volunteer leaders of the mosque sat down with the older suspect","depth":12},{"id":244,"text":"and gave him a clear choice :","depth":13},{"id":245,"text":"either he stops interrupting sermons","depth":15},{"id":246,"text":"and remains silent","depth":15},{"id":247,"text":"or he would not be welcomed , ''","depth":14},{"id":248,"text":"it said .","depth":10},{"id":249,"text":"`` While he continued to attend some of the congregational prayers after the January incident ,","depth":9},{"id":250,"text":"he neither interrupted another sermon","depth":10},{"id":251,"text":"nor did he cause any other disturbances . ''","depth":10},{"id":252,"text":"Tamerlan Tsarnaev `` began coming intermittently to our congregational prayers on Friday over a year ago and occasionally to our daily prayers , ''","depth":9},{"id":253,"text":"the statement read .","depth":9},{"id":254,"text":"`` The younger suspect was rarely seen at the center ,","depth":9},{"id":255,"text":"coming only occasionally for prayer . ''","depth":9},{"id":256,"text":"One of the victims , Krystle Campbell was memorialized Monday morning in a service at St. Joseph Catholic Church in Medford , Massachusetts .","depth":7},{"id":257,"text":"After the service , police officers lined the street in front of the church","depth":9},{"id":258,"text":"as other officers","depth":11},{"id":259,"text":"wearing dress uniforms","depth":11},{"id":260,"text":"saluted","depth":10},{"id":261,"text":"as the casket","depth":11},{"id":262,"text":"bearing her remains","depth":11},{"id":263,"text":"was taken from the church","depth":10},{"id":264,"text":"and loaded into a hearse .","depth":9},{"id":265,"text":"Another memorial service was scheduled Monday night at Boston University for Lingzi Lu , a student from China .","depth":8},{"id":266,"text":"Lu was a graduate student in mathematics and statistics .","depth":9},{"id":267,"text":"Before coming to Boston ,","depth":10},{"id":268,"text":"she won an academic scholarship to the Beijing Institute of Technology ,","depth":11},{"id":269,"text":"where she received accolades for her math skills .","depth":11},{"id":270,"text":"On Wednesday , Vice President Joe Biden will attend the memorial service for MIT police officer Sean Collier ,","depth":8},{"id":271,"text":"who was allegedly killed by the Tsarnaev brothers .","depth":8},{"id":272,"text":"A week after the marathon bombings , 50 people remain hospitalized ,","depth":9},{"id":273,"text":"including two in critical condition ,","depth":9},{"id":274,"text":"according to a CNN tally .","depth":8},{"id":275,"text":"Patients at Boston Medical Center have received visits from war veterans","depth":9},{"id":276,"text":"who have also suffered amputations .","depth":9},{"id":277,"text":"The vets ,","depth":12},{"id":278,"text":"Dr. Jeffrey Kalish said ,","depth":12},{"id":279,"text":"told patients","depth":11},{"id":280,"text":"that their lives are n't over","depth":11},{"id":281,"text":"because they 've lost limbs .","depth":11},{"id":282,"text":"`` We 've seen really tremendous success and great attitudes , ''","depth":10},{"id":283,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":284,"text":"Also Monday , Davis","depth":10},{"id":285,"text":"-- the Boston police commissioner --","depth":10},{"id":286,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":287,"text":"transit system police officer Richard Donohue ,","depth":10},{"id":288,"text":"wounded in the firefight with the Tsarnaev brothers ,","depth":10},{"id":289,"text":"was improving .","depth":9},{"id":290,"text":"`` He was in grave condition","depth":10},{"id":291,"text":"when he went to the hospital ,","depth":10},{"id":292,"text":"so we 're very optimistic at this point in time ,","depth":10},{"id":293,"text":"and our prayers are with him and his family , ''","depth":10},{"id":294,"text":"he said .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":589,"left":298,"right":588,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":298,"left":0,"right":297,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":297,"left":1,"right":296,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":296,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":588,"left":396,"right":587,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":396,"left":342,"right":395,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":342,"left":328,"right":341,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":328,"left":299,"right":327,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":299,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":327,"left":6,"right":326,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":326,"left":317,"right":325,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":317,"left":313,"right":316,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":313,"left":305,"right":312,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":305,"left":302,"right":304,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":301,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":7,"right":300,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":300,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":304,"left":303,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":312,"left":311,"right":21,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":308,"right":310,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":308,"left":307,"right":17,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":307,"left":14,"right":306,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":310,"left":309,"right":20,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":309,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":316,"left":22,"right":315,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":315,"left":23,"right":314,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":314,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":325,"left":324,"right":34,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":324,"left":26,"right":323,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":323,"left":27,"right":322,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":322,"left":319,"right":321,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":319,"left":28,"right":318,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":318,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":321,"left":31,"right":320,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":320,"left":32,"right":33,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":341,"left":331,"right":340,"relation":"elaboratio